public.users_used_storage.definition: select (storage.foldername("name"))[1] as "user_id", COALESCE(SUM(("metadata"->>'size')::bigint), 0) as "total_size" from "storage"."objects" where "storage"."objects"."bucket_id" = 'assets' group by (storage.foldername("storage"."objects"."name"))[1]
public.users_used_storage.name: users_used_storage
